org.jivesoftware.util
接口 PropertyEventListener

public interface PropertyEventListener

Interface to listen for property events. Use the PropertyEventDispatcher.addListener(PropertyEventListener) method to register for events.

作者：
Matt Tucker

propertySet

void propertySet(java.lang.String property,
                 java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> params)

参数：
property - the name of the property.
params - event parameters.
